Service.create!(name: 'Virtual Functional Medicine', description: 'In this virtual session, I can offer a Functional medicine consultation tailored to your specific needs. Helping you to unravel your complicated health issue. Before the first visit, it is very helpful to receive a Health Assessment Questionnaire and any blood/lab work you have received in the past, so that I may be ready to discuss what your concerns are. This could be for you or your pet. Also, if the visit is for body pain, joint issues, etc., and I cannot see you in person, there are options! With a virtual appointment, we can go over exercises, self therapy, nutritional (anti-inflammatory) needs. I can guide you to a healthier, more vibrant self just over email and, live/virtual (face-to-face) session or phone consult.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 20, duration: 60, practitioner_specialty_id: 1)
Service.create!(name: 'Functional Medicine', description: 'I can offer a Functional medicine consultation tailored to your specific needs. Helping you to unravel your complicated health issue. Before the first visit, it is very helpful to receive a Health Assessment Questionnaire and any blood/lab work you have received in the past, so that I may be ready to discuss what your concerns are. This could be for you or your pet. Also, if the visit is for body pain, joint issues, etc., and I cannot see you in person, there are options! With a virtual appointment, we can go over exercises, self therapy, nutritional (anti-inflammatory) needs. I can guide you to a healthier, more vibrant self just over email and, live/virtual (face-to-face) session or phone consult.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 30, duration: 60, practitioner_specialty_id: 1)
Service.create!(name: 'Wellness Coaching', description: 'Kindred Spirits wellness coaching is designed to assist you (the client) with discovering what your "personalized wellness" looks and feels like. First, complete an assessment questionnaire that helps determine what wellness goals you want to work towards as well as if Kindred Spirits services are a good match. Next, we have our first 1-hour session where a wellness destination is agreed upon, and a map (plan or care) to the destination is developed. Weekly sessions are scheduled to discuss progress, navigating obstacles, and the next steps. Finally, when you are ready we have our final session to discuss overall changes and future plans to maintain any lifestyle changes. *Each session will begin with a clearing process. *We will address mental, physical and spiritual elements in each session. *Coaching is a journey that the client and practitioner take together!', service_type: 'In-person', price: 40, duration: 75, practitioner_specialty_id: 2)
Service.create!(name: 'Remote Wellness Coaching', description: 'This is remote session! Kindred Spirits wellness coaching is designed to assist you (the client) with discovering what your "personalized wellness" looks and feels like. First, complete an assessment questionnaire that helps determine what wellness goals you want to work towards as well as if Kindred Spirits services are a good match. Next, we have our first 1-hour session where a wellness destination is agreed upon, and a map (plan or care) to the destination is developed. Weekly sessions are scheduled to discuss progress, navigating obstacles, and the next steps. Finally, when you are ready we have our final session to discuss overall changes and future plans to maintain any lifestyle changes. *Each session will begin with a clearing process. *We will address mental, physical and spiritual elements in each session. *Coaching is a journey that the client and practitioner take together!', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 50, duration: 75, practitioner_specialty_id: 2)
Service.create!(name: 'Guided Imagery And Mediation', description: 'Guided Imagery and Meditation is a slightly deeper form of meditation than one may practice on thier own. The goal is to allow the guide to assist you in navigating the terrain of you "soul filter" (a woven filter composed of your experiences, thoughts, and emotions) for the purpose of addressing matters which may be subconsciously stimuli for your actions or reactions on your conscious plane of existence. In a session, the clients (you) will be asked to assume a comfortable position, close your eyes and focus on your breath. The guide (me) will assist you through verbal ques with finding your mental safe place and from there the journey into your "soul filter" will begin. While on the journey I will steer your focus towards detail which may be of significance. The journey culminated when you are comfortably able to return to thier normal state of consciousness. The information gathered while on our journey will be discussed immediately upon return. *Reiki and clearing are offered after the session if the client is interested. * The State of California does not license Reiki Practitioners', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 100, duration: 30, practitioner_specialty_id: 3)
Service.create!(name: 'Nutritional Coaching', description: 'Nutritional Coaching sessions can be limited to guidance for weight, mental, emotional, or physical health conditions or can include virtual cooking classes. For those who strictly want support, traditional coaching techniques are utilized. We (the client and the practitioner) will start will an assessment session. This is where you (the client) will express your goals and what you want to gain from our coaching sessions. From here we will map out (create a plan of care) our route to your nutritional wellness destination. We will schedule weekly sessions for the purpose of guidance, progress updates, and support. Once the destination has been reached a plan to maintain any lifestyle changes is created and when you are comfortable the coaching is considered complete. The option of virtual cooking classes is also offered for those who want to learn ways to maximized thier nutritional coaching experience with healthy cooking alternatives.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 20, duration: 180, practitioner_specialty_id: 3)
Service.create!(name: '1:1 Life Coaching', description: 'Easily and quickly get to the core root cause of unwanted behaviors and outcomes through unlocking the power of your unconscious mind by retraining your brain to deliberately create more of what you want in your life (and less of what you don\'t) both personally and professionally to get your desired outcomes and results.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 30, duration: 45, practitioner_specialty_id: 4)
Service.create!(name: 'Initial Nutrition Assessment', description: 'Full assessment, determine priorities , discuss how we can support you with nutrition , determine any further testing / labs needed, etc.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 40, duration: 135, practitioner_specialty_id: 4)
Service.create!(name: 'Craniosacral Therapy', description: 'Craniosacral Therapy is a body work modality that begins at the base layer of the physical body and offers relief and healing from many everyday maladies. The Craniosacral system is made up of the bones of the head, spinal cord and sacrum (which is the flat bone at the base of the spine). The bones, muscles and tissues of the body hold stress and restriction and can become compressed and unbalanced.A Craniosacral Therapist is trained to feel with the hands the motion of the Craniosacral system as a unified, integrated movement. The gentlest of approaches is often more powerful than the most robust. Conditions Craniosacral Therapy can help to relieve: Stress and the “busy” mind Fatigue Fibromyalgia Anxiety Hyperactivity Sinus and allergy Headaches and migraines Depression Memory problems TMJ and tooth pain Ear infection Vertigo Imbalances in the nervous system ADD/ADHD Craniosacral Therapy can be very beneficial for children and adults with ADD or ADHD. Craniosacral Therapy helps to rebalance the rhythm of the body and organize the activity of the mind thereby allowing an improved, more balanced landscape for the individual to operate from. The energetic aspect of Craniosacral Therapy also plays a part in creating a new, improved, more balanced mind/body environment. What to expect in a session Wear comfortable clothing, such as cotton or a sweat suit, when receiving a craniosacral session. Sessions last approximately 1 hour to 1 hour and 15 minutes in length. The person will rest comfortably face up on padded treatment table with eyes closed and will remain fully clothed. Soothing music and a peaceful, relaxing environment is offered during the session. The treatments are painless and the craniosacral therapist uses only gentle touch', service_type: 'In-person', price: 50, duration: 150, practitioner_specialty_id: 5)
Service.create!(name: 'Acupuncture & Herbal Consultation', description: 'One session includes one hour of very gentle and light touch acupuncture with a short full body light massage to finish. Depending on the patient’s diagnosis, there may be herbal consultation and prescription to treat the condition and to help further heal the patient.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 25, duration: 30, practitioner_specialty_id: 5)
Service.create!(name: 'Remote Craniosacral Therapy Session', description: 'A Remote session can be done in the comfort of your own home or wherever you happen to be. A brief phone conversation between receiver and therapist will begin the session, followed by a 55 min period of relaxation/rest by the receiver. During this time, the therapist connects on an energetic level with the receiver and the session takes place. Upon therapists completion of session, the receiver and therapist speak again over phone and share their experience. By utilizing the unlimited capacity of the energy body, (which is comprised of the physical, emotional/mental and spiritual bodies), the receiver and therapist connect and release, relief and healing is offered in a way that transcends the physical plane.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 30, duration: 75, practitioner_specialty_id: 6)
Service.create!(name: 'Eft (Emotional Freedom Techniques)', description: 'EFT and Matrix Re-imprinting can create significant shifts in your life. It allows you to identify any blocks preventing you from living from a place of joy. These techniques are used to release the past so you can move in a positive direction. We will identify existing belief systems or negative memories that limit you from living your most authentic life. EFT & Matrix Re-imprinting ﻿can be a surprisingly easy and gentle process. I\'ll give you words to re﻿peat and show you exactly where to tap by tapping along with you. We\'ll stop often to check our progress. Even if intense emotions arise, they tend to be discharged quickly allowing for immediate relief. Key memories may surface, leading us to transition into Matrix Re-imprinting. This form of EFT allows us to help the younger self that is trapped within the memory. This profound work allows us to access and change the negative beliefs, making room for greater clarity and insight.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 50, duration: 90, practitioner_specialty_id: 6)
Service.create!(name: 'Eft (Emotional Freedom Techniques) For Anxiety: Tapping For Tension', description: 'EFT is an amazing tool to reduce cortisol levels (stress hormone) and our stress response (fight/flight). When adrenaline kicks in, it causes fear/anxiety to take over of bodies/minds. We will tap together to "turn down the volume" of the stress response. Tapping has a direct and immediate effect on parts of the brain that control fight/flight. We will move these emotions through the body so they can be discharged quickly. This will enable you to feel lighter and function more effectively in your daily life.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 40, duration: 105, practitioner_specialty_id: 7)
Service.create!(name: 'Meditation And Breathwork Video Class', description: 'This is a 15 to 30 minute instructional meditation video. I assign each meditation based on the student’s needs. This can also be a preview of my teaching style for a longer 90-minute yoga & meditstion class or private session. You will also have access to an email question and answer session with me to answer your questions about the class.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 45, duration: 120, practitioner_specialty_id: 7)
Service.create!(name: 'Yoga - breath focused vinyasa flow', description: 'The main purpose of the session is to create a safe, peaceful environment in which the client can mindfully focus on their breath and movement as a form of meditation. The yoga session will start with an assessment of the client\'s well being to create an individualized practice. There will be a strong emphasis on breathing techniques throughout the session. The vinyasa practice will flow based on the client\'s level of experience. There will be hands-on adjustment(s) if agreeable by the client. Afterward there will be feedback to the practitioner and client to help steer further practice together.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 70, duration: 135, practitioner_specialty_id: 8)
Service.create!(name: 'Holistic Health Coaching - wellness assessment', description: 'The wellness assessment is the initial session to have the opportunity to get to know the client in a comprehensive way. This can be done both in person or virtually (video conference). I will convey that as an Adult Nurse Practitioner I would like to be an adjunct to their medical care and provide education and resources to help them navigate their health. This is the first of 3-6 sessions based on their needs. I will provide ongoing support and helpful information for them to help take control of their health concerns. The holistic health coaching should be viewed as a continuum of care. The opportunity to build rapport and trust with a licensed, experienced health care provider that can be a strong resource for them.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 75, duration: 150, practitioner_specialty_id: 8)
Service.create!(name: 'Health-Wellness & Fitness', description: 'At the time of an appointment with my clients, I will be conducting either a computerized or paper assessment. there is one assessment for personal training/group fitness and their is one assessment for wellness coaching. in my personal training and group fitness assessments, their will be general questions, that I will ask my clients to answer based on their level of knowledge that they have on their own personal health and fitness level. for wellness coaching appointments the process will be pretty similar but, the questions will be pertaining to the ten dimensions of health and wellness. the appointment times and time limits for clients to set appointments will range anywhere from 30-60 minutes or a 1hr, and the rates and prices will be based on the amount of time that is being spent in each appointment.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 80, duration: 165, practitioner_specialty_id: 9)
Service.create!(name: 'Holistic Health Coach Session ', description: 'A Holistic Health Coach is a guide and mentor who empowers you, and provides ongoing support and guidance as you set goals and make sustainable changes that improve your health and happiness. As your Holistic Health Coach, Melanie offers a support system that is unique to your needs. She will help you create an organic and whole food-based diet that works best for your body and lifestyle, as well as a regular routine that is both manageable and environmentally-friendly. Together, you will co-create completely personalized actions to move you toward your ideal vision of health within your unique body, lifestyle, preferences, and resources. Melanie will be there to listen and support you through your growth, and to hold you accountable to your action steps.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 100, duration: 180, practitioner_specialty_id: 9)
Service.create!(name: 'Holistic Massage Therapy', description: 'I practice intuitive and integrative bodywork. I work with clients to customize sessions based on their needs and goals of the session. I combine various techniques from my toolkit to provide unique therapeutic bodywork sessions that aid the body\'s innate ability to heal itself. I incorporate swedish, shiatsu, acupressure, energy work and essential oils.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 30, duration: 45, practitioner_specialty_id: 10)
Service.create!(name: 'Holistic Nutrition Consultation', description: 'We\'ll discuss your current health status, health issues that are challenging you, and set up a nutritional plan to address the underlying causes. Using targeted nutrients, finding triggers, and adding in specific foods, you\'ll come away with a number of recommendations for diet and lifestyle to start you on your way toward greater health. Practical tips and strategies make simple shifts will be given and customized to your needs.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 50, duration: 90, practitioner_specialty_id: 10)
Service.create!(name: 'Nutrition Deep Dive', description: 'These 4 sessions will provide you with thorough education, support, meal plans, lifestyle tips, and accountability over a 2 month period. Suggested for those looking to heal more chronic issues and looking to make long-lasting changes. Specific recommendations and plans will be created just for your health needs and goals.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 40, duration: 60, practitioner_specialty_id: 11)
Service.create!(name: 'Life Coaching', description: 'During your first appointment, we create larger goals in a variety of different areas in your life and discuss when we want these accomplished. We discuss what barriers you often face and how to hurdle them. We reflect on your strengths. Together we will come up with our first stepping stone for those bigger goals. You will be held accountable throughout the week to these goals. Each week we touch base on your successes, barriers and how to continue to achieve and move forward. This is a very inspiring and motivating process. This process really gives you a coach in life- a life coach.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 45, duration: 30, practitioner_specialty_id: 11)
Service.create!(name: 'One on One Coaching Program', description: 'I create coaching packages designed specifically for the client. Based on your specific needs, we will work together to create a road map of success. Packages range from monthly to annually and are priced accordingly.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 50, duration: 45, practitioner_specialty_id: 12)
Service.create!(name: 'Yoga for Balance', description: 'This is an introductory yoga session tailored to your needs.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 70, duration: 75, practitioner_specialty_id: 12)
Service.create!(name: 'Spiritual & Life Coaching', description: 'Are your aware that your mind is highly hackable? Today is your day to learn everything you need to know to make sure you control what\'s going through your mind & what you are creating for your future. Have you wondered why you keep repeating the same patterns? Yes, your subconscious mind & beliefs are making things happen for you. These beliefs could be preventing you from achieving your highest level of success in your career, family, outside relationships & your inner-self or inner-peace. Success comes in different forms, don\'t be fooled!!!! ...start from Within', service_type: 'In-person', price: 50, duration: 30, practitioner_specialty_id: 13)
Service.create!(name: 'Acupuncture and Cupping Session', description: 'Like a network of rivers nourishing a landscape, the meridians are the channels through which “Qi” flows, to nourish and energize the human body. These channels exist within the subtle body and returns the body to a state of equilibrium and wellness. Though they may have a correspondence to the physical nervous system, you won’t find the meridians per se on an operating table! Collectively, the meridians form the matrix within which the physical body functions. They also act as a network of communication between the physical and the more subtle energetic bodies. Combinations of acupuncture points reset physiology gone awry to invigorate the expulsion of harmful pathogenic agents causing symptoms. I am as a guide, physically, mentally, and spiritually helping you transition during a meaningful time of life. Assisting you to find freedom in a moment, uncovering that next iteration of yourself in a very connected way. Supporting you in healing whatever situation you come in with.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 30, duration: 45, practitioner_specialty_id: 13)
Service.create!(name: 'Yoga Therapeutics Session', description: 'A balanced body encourages balanced thinking. An organic body that functions well results in intelligent evolution. Yoga encourages a skillful means of developing balance, strength and depth. A tool to learn more about the Self and the world. If you have an injury we can explore yoga therapeutics which re-engages the body’s natural healing mechanism through the use of yoga asana (postures) and breath-work. This comprehensive approach supports specific areas of the body to heal, as well as strengthening the body systemically so you can recover from injuries, surgery or a variety of stress-related disorders. In practice we will explore you in the personal and seasonal, taking into consideration any injuries or concerns, at any level, at any time of your life!', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 80, duration: 75, practitioner_specialty_id: 14)
Service.create!(name: 'Chiropractic Session', description: 'Chiropractic appointments will include a full spinal and musckuloskeltal assessment. Soft tissue therapies in various forms including percussion therapy, cupping, and myofascial releases will be delivered if deemed necessary. Spinal manipulation and corrective exercises will follow. Finally, lifestyle modifications will be discussed at the end of the session. The time spent on each portion of this session will vary based on the patient.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 15, duration: 120, practitioner_specialty_id: 14)
Service.create!(name: 'Mind Body Collective', description: 'In the Mind Body Collective, we will discuss how the attention and direction of the mind can affect the physical body. Sessions will begin with a lengthly emotional health history. We will take time to identify what may be ailing the mind and in turn affecting the body. Sessions will include identification and understanding of topics such as: the intuition vs. the ego, neurotransmitters, spiritual connectedness and mindfulness.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 90, duration: 135, practitioner_specialty_id: 15)
Service.create!(name: 'Functional Medicine Consultation', description: 'Functional Medicine sessions vary based on the patient. Anything from fatigue, gastrointestinal difficulties, thyroid dysfunction, autoimmune, and headaches may be treated with functional medicine. Sessions will begin with an intensive health history discussion and end with lifestyle modifications. As sessions continue, certain labs such as blood panels or hormone tests may be ordered in order to better asses the physiology of the condition. Further, supplements and dietary patterns will be recommended to the patient based specifically off of their condition and lab work.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 35, duration: 180, practitioner_specialty_id: 15)
Service.create!(name: 'Private Virtual Reiki Session', description: 'Reiki is a natural universal energy that permeates all beings. In this session we will work to channel the energy towards its highest good in you and encourage self healing. Either seated or lying down, the client rests in a meditative state while the practitioner offers hovered hands (no touch) above various energy channels of the body. Clients have experienced relaxation of the muscles, release of emotions, calming of the nervous system and overall improved mental clarity following sessions. Experiencing the Reiki energy is different for everyone and is not always apparent; the energy goes where it is most needed. Feeling the affects a few days after our session? Email or text any questions or experiences and I will be happy to provide feedback and support. All new clients receive a complimentary phone consultation and 15 minute introductory session for us to get to know each other and understand your aspirations.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 50, duration: 150, practitioner_specialty_id: 16)
Service.create!(name: 'Private Reiki Session', description: 'Reiki is a natural universal energy that permeates all beings. In this session we will work to channel the energy towards its highest good in you and encourage self healing. Either seated or lying down, the client rests in a meditative state while the practitioner offers hovered hands (no touch) above various energy channels of the body. Clients have experienced relaxation of the muscles, release of emotions, calming of the nervous system and overall improved mental clarity following sessions. Experiencing the Reiki energy is different for everyone and is not always apparent; the energy goes where it is most needed. Feeling the affects a few days after our session? Email or text any questions or experiences and I will be happy to provide feedback and support. All new clients receive a complimentary phone consultation and 15 minute introductory session for us to get to know each other and understand your aspirations.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 60, duration: 150, practitioner_specialty_id: 16)
Service.create!(name: 'Nutrition Consultation', description: 'In this phone call, Skype session, or Zoom call, we’ll discuss your health history and I’ll recommend what I think would work best for your specific needs. We\'ll discuss your eating habits, lifestyle changes, and more.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 30, duration: 60, practitioner_specialty_id: 17)
Service.create!(name: 'HEALTH + LIFESTYLE COACHING SESSION', description: 'During the INITIAL HEALTH + LIFESTYLE COACHING SESSION, together we assess your health history, nutrition, daily habits, current fitness practice, discuss challenges, and establish goals. Sessions following the initial consultation are focused on support and accountability. For lasting lifestyle changes and results, it is recommended to commit to a 3 MONTH PROGRAM meeting weekly or a 6 MONTH PROGRAM meeting bi-weekly. Sessions are personalized and unique to your personal challenges and goals.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 45, duration: 45, practitioner_specialty_id: 17)
Service.create!(name: 'Beginners Vinyasa Yoga Flow', description: 'Beginners Vinyasa Yoga Flow is an introduction to the core elements of vinyasa yoga (linking breath with each movement between poses). We walk through a step-by-step of basic warm-up poses, vinyasa flows, foundational poses, restorative poses, and breath work, with light meditation if preferred. I\'m happy to provide hands-on assists if that is something you are comfortable with. You will leave with a better understanding of the benefits of yoga pertaining to both the mind and body, and poses you can take home to practice.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 100, duration: 135, practitioner_specialty_id: 18)
Service.create!(name: 'Intermediate Yoga Vinyasa Flow', description: 'Intermediate Yoga Vinyasa Flow provides experience yogis with a deeper level of asana modifications, mixed within a vinyasa flow. You can choose which poses you\'re working towards that you\'d like me to incorporate, or I can provide my own after assessing your flow. Common intermediate poses include headstand, tripod, binds, one-legged balancing poses, scorpion, wheel, crow variations, and more. This session is all about fun and non-judgement.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 35, duration: 90, practitioner_specialty_id: 18)
Service.create!(name: 'Breath Work Session', description: 'The Breath Work Session focuses on how our how controlled breathing can help to relax the body and mind and allow for a deeper yoga practice. You can choose to do a full breathing session, or one that links with poses or where your mind is at on that specific day. Please see below for a more detailed description of each breath. Ocean-like nostril breathing (Ujjayi): The foundational breathing technique for vinyasa yoga. Three-part breath (Kumbhaka): Allows you to breath to your full capacity to alleviate anxiety. Alternate nostril breathing (Nadi shodhana): Channels feminine and masculine energy and clearing of mind to set intentions. Breath Retention (Kumbhaka) Helps to focus on the present and be further in touch with your body\'s wants and needs. Fire breath (kapalabhati) Breathing to fire up central nervous system and blood flow.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 60, duration: 105, practitioner_specialty_id: 19)
Service.create!(name: 'One-on-One Platonic Therapeutic Touch', description: 'Touch deprivation can feel like loneliness, stress and a sense of missing something. During a Platonic Therapeutic Touch Session you will enter a nonjudgmental and caring container. Through holding space you will have the opportunity to experience vulnerability, intimacy, self-awareness and touch. This happens by eye gazing, talking, hand holding, affection, hair stroking, communication, crying, synchronized breathing, meditation and providing you with undivided attention. We will also mirror behavior such as consent, acknowledge and respecting boundaries and helping to recognize your needs and becoming confidant in asking for what you want.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 65, duration: 90, practitioner_specialty_id: 19)
Service.create!(name: 'Virtual Human Connection Session', description: 'Maybe you need to blow off a little steam and vent about a problem. Perhaps you are looking for understanding and want to share about a situation. Or, simply, you want to be heard and acknowledged. Now, what if your schedule does not allow for an in-person session? This is a quick and easy way to connect with a practitioner when you cannot make it in for a healing hug.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 25, duration: 30, practitioner_specialty_id: 20)
Service.create!(name: 'Guided Meditation', description: 'We offer guided meditation and deep relaxation. Options for meditation include restorative stretch and meditation, sitting meditation, full body scan meditation, self-kindness meditation, guided meditation to music, or seated meditation in silence. Our spaces are designed for optimum relaxation and focus.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 30, duration: 45, practitioner_specialty_id: 20)
Service.create!(name: 'RapidSculpt EMS', description: 'RapidSculpt EMS is a 20 minute total body strength and endurance training program followed by a 10 minute muscle recovery program. The entire session takes approximately 45 minutes. Clients must bring athletic shoes, water and a face towel. FireSnake Fitness provides the specialized training suit that must be worn during the training. Prior to beginning the session, a comprehensive health assessment and discussion about fitness/lifestyle/nutrition goals will be completed with the client.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 15, duration: 60, practitioner_specialty_id: 21)
Service.create!(name: 'FireSculpt Class', description: 'FireSculpt is a 35-minute total-body strength training class that uses dumbbells, body-weight and cardio bursts to tone and sculpt the body. All movements are synced to music which makes it incredibly fun! Modifications are offered for almost all exercises so that all clients can achieve success, no matter their fitness level or limitations. Virtual classes are $20/class.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 100, duration: 120, practitioner_specialty_id: 21)
Service.create!(name: 'Yoga For Fertility', description: 'We begin each session with a check in as to where you are in your cycle or treatment journey. We discuss what and where you would like to focus of the session to be, and move into a series of restorative poses to fully benefit your reproductive health. We end the session with a meditation focused on what we have worked on, where we are, and where you want to be moving forward. Using breath and visualization techniques, we will end the session calm, restored, and full of hope.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 35, duration: 135, practitioner_specialty_id: 22)
Service.create!(name: 'Prenatal Yoga', description: 'I am here to hold the space for you as you grow into this new role of parent. I hear and see the challenges you face with physical and emotional discomforts of pregnancy and the postpartum period. I offer prenatal yoga sessions to help bring more ease to your body and mind and preparing you for a more comfortable pregnancy and helping you heal and strengthen postpartum.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 50, duration: 180, practitioner_specialty_id: 22)
Service.create!(name: 'The Roarrior Shift Embodied Mentorship', description: 'The above price represents a 4 session package of 1 - on - 1 spiritually bold mentorship, that decodes life\'s invisible obstacles through ancestral mediumship, identifying dream & personality patterning through intersectional behavioral breath and embodied techniques. Lastly postural and core awareness support through tailored goal planning. Most clients work with me for a minimum to three to six months on an intended goal. Where my keen awareness is utilized as a spiritual support and guide towards you maintaining optimal presence to complete your heroes journey and RISE AT LAST!', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 30, duration: 30, practitioner_specialty_id: 23)
Service.create!(name: 'Flex Form Pilates Session', description: 'The first few sessions are focused on learning the breathing technique while doing introductory movements on the reformer. Breath first, Body second. During these sessions a person becomes aware of using sensory perception to tell the Brain how to adjust the Body to create proper form. It can be considered as a physically active form of meditation.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 40, duration: 30, practitioner_specialty_id: 23)
Service.create!(name: 'Chi Qong Neck and Shoulders Body Work', description: 'The Pilates session is for the specific needs of the runner, which will improve their performance and running technique to prevent injuries, thus strengthening the deep muscles associated with running', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 45, duration: 60, practitioner_specialty_id: 24)
Service.create!(name: 'Pilates for runners', description: 'The Pilates session is for the specific needs of the runner, which will improve their performance and running technique to prevent injuries, thus strengthening the deep muscles associated with running', service_type: 'In-person', price: 55, duration: 30, practitioner_specialty_id: 24)
Service.create!(name: 'Sports Medicine + Health Coaching Session', description: 'At this time, all of my health coaching and sports medicine practice is conducted virtually. I can promise a positive experience and uplifting coaching sessions, free from judgement. I always hope to help clients feel comfortable and happy as a result of their coaching session. I provide a clean, welcoming atmosphere I would keep a judgement free zone and make sure that clients felt comfortable and happy as a result of their visit. I find that people want time. A 10 minute visit won\'t always cut it when a person really needs your guidance and treatment and so I schedule at least a half hour per client.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 65, duration: 45, practitioner_specialty_id: 25)
Service.create!(name: 'Couples Coaching with Hypnotherapy', description: 'll sessions are completed via Skype call. First part will always be coaching session, last portion if hypnoses or meditation is need will be at the end of the session. Things that will be needed based on type of session. - Either a laptop, a desktop computer, a tablet. - A webcam - Internet connection - A headset with earphones - Needed for hypnotherapy or meditation clients. A comfortable chair or sofa you will sit on facing the computer device, close enough that I have a good visual of your whole face.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 30, duration: 60, practitioner_specialty_id: 25)
Service.create!(name: 'Express Coaching Session', description: 'Express Coaching for Key Roadblocks is a solution-focused method, for quickly and easily getting you to the heart of your process, condition, or challenge. Sessions focus on a key situation or roadblock to help expand your choices. You naturally engage inner wisdom and apply your strengths allowing you to apply clarity, energy, and action when you need it most.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 55, duration: 75, practitioner_specialty_id: 26)
